data.description: Salt Creek runs through this beautiful 2.5 acre property! A 2007, 1560sq ft.  2 bed/2 bath manufactured home with a large deck, large 900 ft detached shop/garage, RV Parking, storage shed and more! Open Kitchen concept with nice sized living room and additional office space.Raised garden beds, fruit trees and plenty of room to expand! Close to town yet feel removed in the quiet countryside and easy access to the Olympic National Park! Don't miss out on this lovely oasis! Crescent Water and individual well on property.
